GitHubApiData.name: PokedexUI
GitHubApiData.description: A simple Pokedex app written in SwiftUI that implements the PokeAPI, using Swift Concurrency, MVVM architecture and pagination

TranslatedDescriptions.zh-CN: 一个使用SwiftUI编写的简单宝可梦图鉴应用，集成了PokeAPI，采用Swift并发、MVVM架构和分页功能。
TranslatedDescriptions.ja: Swift Concurrency、MVVMアーキテクチャ、ページネーションを使用し、PokeAPIを実装したSwiftUI製のシンプルなポケモン図鑑アプリです。
TranslatedDescriptions.ko: Swift Concurrency, MVVM 아키텍처 및 페이지네이션을 사용하여 PokeAPI를 구현한 SwiftUI 기반 간단한 포켓덱스 앱입니다.
TranslatedDescriptions.en: A simple Pokedex app written in SwiftUI that utilizes the PokeAPI, incorporating Swift Concurrency, MVVM architecture, and pagination.
TranslatedDescriptions.es: Una aplicación sencilla de Pokedex escrita en SwiftUI que implementa la PokeAPI, utilizando Swift Concurrency, arquitectura MVVM y paginación.
TranslatedDescriptions.fr: Une application Pokedex simple écrite en SwiftUI qui utilise la PokeAPI, avec la concurrence Swift, l'architecture MVVM et la pagination.
